_a street with a portland cement concrete, asphaltic concrete, or bituminous wearing surface or other hard surfaces
which are acceptable and suitable to the local public body for use with local climate, soil, gradient, and volume and
character of traffic. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
All-weather
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

