_a street that can be used year-round with a minimum of maintenance, such as the use of a grader and minor application
of surface material, and is acceptable and suitable to the local public body for use with local climate, soil, gradient,
and volume and character of traffic. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

