for three informal rulemaking hearings that will be held on all issues raised by the proposal. The dates of these hearings
have been changed. This notice sets the new dates and specific locations of the informal public hearings to be held
as part of the rulemaking process. In addition, it extends the original date for the submission of Notices of Intention
to Appear by three weeks and reduces the time frame for the submission of documentary evidence and the text of lengthy
testimony from 21 days to 14 days prior to the date of the hearing where the evidence will be presented.
