<!-- PJG ITAG l=81 g=1 f=1 -->
2. New Classifications: (i) ``Volunteer'' (Class H) and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) Volunteer or Contractor Employee Who Is Classified as a ``Worker on Duty'' (Class A)
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

