Injuries or illnesses sustained by such a volunteer would be reported on Form FRA F 6180.55a as injuries to a ``Volunteer''
(Class H). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
In contrast, injuries or illnesses sustained by an individual, including a ``volunteer'' or ``contractor employee,''
who is engaged in either (i) the operation of on-track equipment or (ii) any other safety-sensitive function for the
