and to update changes in the status of a particular case. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
c. Elimination of supplementary record required under &sect;225.25(b). 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
FRA has found that much of the information requested in the supplementary record of injuries and illnesses pursuant
to the present regulation set forth in &sect;225.25(b) would be collected on the new ``Railroad Worker Injury and
Illness Log'' as proposed in &sect;225.25(a). Therefore, the requirement that each railroad maintain a supplementary
