<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Proposed &sect;225.25(e)(1) outlines the data that would be included in the list. New &sect;225.25(e)(2) proposes
that if no reportable injuries or illnesses were associated with an establishment, the posting shall make reference
to that fact. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
e. 
