<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
B. Storm/lightning damage. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
C. Vandalism. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
